ASCENSION RULES:
When a Character you control Ascends, they gain one of the following Abilities of your choice based on their colour.
Characters cannot Ascend more than once.

WHITE:
- The first Attack used by this Character each turn costs -2.
- When this Character deals DMG, you may play a Character card from your hand with 3 or less Energy Cost without paying that cost.

BLACK:
- When this Character Attacks, you may move a card you control from play to your Discard Pile.
- [2][T] - KO a friendly Character, draw 2 cards.

RED:
- When this Character Attacks, you may put a card from your hand in your Energy Zone, that card is removed when Tapped.
- When this Character Attacks, it deals 20 extra damage per Character below full HP you control.

BLUE:
- [T] - Draw a card.
- One of this Character's Abilites gains [Intercept] (You decide which one)

YELLOW:
- When this Character deals DMG to an enemy Character, you may select one of that Character's ablities, it loses that ability until your next Start Phase.
- [1][T] - Redirect an Attack to this Character, the Attack deals no damage. [Once per Game](This Ability can only be selected Once per Game)

GREEN:
- [T] - Heal this Character fully, put a [DMG - BOOST 10] Counter on it for each 30 HP healed this way. [Once per Game]
- During your Start Phase, this Character heals for 30 HP and you may pay [2], if you do, This Character takes 20 less DMG from Attacks until your next Start Phase.

PURPLE:
- Put a [DMG Boost - 20] Counter on this Character during your End Phase and every following Start Phase.
- [3][T] - Move your [DMG Boost] Counters in any way you want.

COLOURLESS:
- [T] - Add [1].
